            <abstract xml:lang="en">
              <p>We propose ECI (Entanglement–Complexity–Information), a phenomenological architecture assembling six independently-established research programs (2022–2026) into a unified predictive canvas: (i) type-II observer-dependent von Neumann algebras via the QRF crossed product; (ii) DESI DR2 dynamical-dark-energy preference at 2.6–3.9 sigma addressed by non-minimally coupled thawing quintessence (xi_chi R chi^2 / 2); (iii) the H0 tension reduced to ~2 sigma by Early Dark Energy with f_EDE = 0.09 ± 0.03; (iv) the Dark Dimension scenario c' ≃ 0.05 as a microscopic dark-matter candidate; (v) Cryptographic Censorship as a selection rule on admissible bulk geometries; (vi) persistent-homology diagnostics of primordial non-Gaussianity. ECI is an architectural synthesis, not a derivation. Axiom A3 (Cryptographic Censorship) is stated as a working conjecture in the cosmological setting. The manuscript is accompanied by symbolic derivations (D1–D6) and numerical sanity checks (N1–N5) in the companion repository.</p>
            </abstract>
